{
  "name": "Expanded Focus",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/cross-circle-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Class</p><p>Prerequisite: At least 4+ levels in Weapon Specialist</p><p> </p><p>You become able to focus on more than your current limitation of weapon focuses. </p><p>You gain the following benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Select one weapon type, such as Katana's or Kunai, that you have not already marked as a Weapon Focus. <br />This chosen weapon becomes known as your Weapon Focus granting it a +1 bonus to Attack and Damage rolls and a trait. </p><p>• A Weapon Focus can only have a +3 bonus to Attack and Damage rolls as a result of being a Weapon Focus. </p><p>• You can take this Feat more than once, selecting either a new weapon type, or the same weapon you previous selected with this Feat.</p>",
